---
title: Roast Veggie Ribollita with Plant-Based Pesto & Garlic Ciabatta
description: This hearty plant-based veggie soup that's hailed from Tuscany is just what the doctor ordered. With tender cannellini
beans, a finishing of basil pesto and crusty ciabatta, this is the type of recipe that’ll soon become a dinnertime staple.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-veggie-ribollita-e83f5a26.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/roasted-veggie-ribollita-60c0730f7f767d503b24da14-c343285c.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
